01:08:09,110 --> 01:08:11,180
Every time something happens,

777
01:08:11,180 --> 01:08:13,960
why is it only your coworker by your side?

778
01:08:16,200 --> 01:08:18,420
He's not here anymore.

779
01:08:22,110 --> 01:08:25,110
It's not what you think.

780
01:08:25,110 --> 01:08:30,630
In short, he's somewhere very far away.

781
01:08:33,390 --> 01:08:35,790
When is he coming back?

782
01:08:37,380 --> 01:08:39,770
So you guys are separated?

783
01:08:43,990 --> 01:08:46,180
Then what's the problem?

784
01:08:46,180 --> 01:08:47,820
How can you think there's no problem?

785
01:08:47,820 --> 01:08:50,390
I... I've gotten married.

786
01:08:50,390 --> 01:08:53,010
You're single right now, and I'm single too.

787
01:08:53,010 --> 01:08:55,610
So the problem is...?

788
01:08:57,510 --> 01:08:59,750
The problem is

789
01:09:00,780 --> 01:09:05,350
I'm not ready to love someone again.

790
01:09:10,240 --> 01:09:12,960
Then when will you be ready?

791
01:09:14,890 --> 01:09:17,760
Did you think that after hearing your reason,

792
01:09:17,760 --> 01:09:23,490
I was just going to say "I understand" and then quietly leave?

793
01:09:23,490 --> 01:09:27,340
- I—
- You truly underestimate me.

794
01:09:27,340 --> 01:09:29,330
Then what exactly do you want me to do?

795
01:09:29,330 --> 01:09:31,290
Take a good look at your feelings deep inside.

796
01:09:31,290 --> 01:09:33,260
No running away.

797
01:09:35,110 --> 01:09:36,530
That's impossible.

798
01:09:36,530 --> 01:09:40,820
It's possible, because I will make you forget him.

799
01:09:45,800 --> 01:09:48,650
So all of the money that Tianliang lost is here.

800
01:09:48,650 --> 01:09:51,550
As the funds flowed out of Tianliang into unknown companies,

801
01:09:51,550 --> 01:09:55,270
did you happily accept sum after sum?

802
01:09:55,270 --> 01:09:57,450
If you return the money now,

803
01:09:57,450 --> 01:09:59,360
we don't have to investigate this matter any further.

804
01:09:59,360 --> 01:10:01,640
Where is He Tianxing? I looked everywhere for you but couldn't find you.

805
01:10:01,640 --> 01:10:03,310
When I called, no one picked up.

806
01:10:03,310 --> 01:10:06,470
You actually like me. That means I still have a chance.

807
01:10:06,470 --> 01:10:08,950
Zheng Xiao'en, with you in my life,

808
01:10:08,950 --> 01:10:12,380
the storm can truly clear up in my world.

809
01:10:23,390 --> 01:10:26,660
♫ Memories wear protective coloration ♫

810
01:10:26,660 --> 01:10:29,790
♫ Ambushing in the middle of the night ♫

811
01:10:29,790 --> 01:10:35,190
♫ A quiet strike ♫

812
01:10:35,190 --> 01:10:38,390
♫ Streetlights awaiting dusk ♫

813
01:10:38,390 --> 01:10:40,750
♫ Still awaiting as always ♫

814
01:10:40,750 --> 01:10:43,860
♫ Nothing is impossible ♫

815
01:10:43,860 --> 01:10:48,280
♫ Even if no one is perfect ♫

816
01:10:48,280 --> 01:10:52,830
♫ Holding you next to my heartbeat ♫

817
01:10:52,830 --> 01:10:56,010
♫ Tightly held the palm of my hand ♫

818
01:10:56,010 --> 01:11:01,020
♫ It remains the only farewell ♫

819
01:11:01,020 --> 01:11:05,720
♫ If I could see you again ♫

820
01:11:05,720 --> 01:11:12,480
♫ Carefully planning my gamble with you ♫

821
01:11:12,480 --> 01:11:16,590
♫ In the end I lost to you ♫

822
01:11:16,590 --> 01:11:25,770
♫ I think of you until I can no longer breathe ♫

823
01:11:25,770 --> 01:11:29,550
♫ If you were a painter ♫

824
01:11:29,550 --> 01:11:31,530
♫ Then I'll be your canvas ♫

825
01:11:31,530 --> 01:11:35,840
♫ No regrets ♫

826
01:11:35,840 --> 01:11:41,590
♫ I lost all my love to you ♫
